{"id":232945419,"title":"#請益 行動硬碟 Seagate Backup Plus Slim","content":"我從來沒有買過行動硬碟\n爬文很久還是很怕自己買到不好的\n所以想請問大家有沒有用過這款？🙏\n\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/2f358c3d-df6c-4a0b-94f6-99a56db8abb7/full.jpeg\n\n另外也想問一下\n商品敘述寫到：\n「為Mac硬碟機安裝提供的 NTFS 驅動程式，即可在 Windows 和 Mac 電腦之間交互使用硬碟機」\n但我爬文看到有人說安裝驅動後檔案出現問題？\n不過我不確定是不是自己安裝的才會有問題\n如果是seagate產品本身的驅動會比較穩定嗎？\n\n我知道exFAT 可以用在 Windows 和 Mac 電腦\n但是我在找行動硬碟都沒有看到格式的標示\n只有這款是有寫NTFS 加上Mac可以用的驅動程式\n\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/6572339a-c19d-4711-840a-7362780d3c1c/full.jpeg\n我找了好多資料都還是搞不太懂的感覺\n所以才來這裡 po文求助⋯\n真的很謝謝願意點進來的大家🙏","excerpt":"我從來沒有買過行動硬碟，爬文很久還是很怕自己買到不好的，所以想請問大家有沒有用過這款？另外也想問一下，商品敘述寫到：「為Mac硬碟機安裝提供的 NTFS 驅動程式，即可在 Windows 和 Mac ","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"0e0bc27b-8c69-4149-b229-04e7a865a09d","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-23T14:02:02.621Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-23T14:02:02.621Z","commentCount":5,"likeCount":3,"tags":[],"topics":["行動硬碟"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"3C","forumAlias":"3c","school":"文藻外語大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":3}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/2f358c3d-df6c-4a0b-94f6-99a56db8abb7/full.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/6572339a-c19d-4711-840a-7362780d3c1c/full.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"6c678b88-473d-4785-a917-2d393cdad760","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/2f358c3d-df6c-4a0b-94f6-99a56db8abb7/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/2f358c3d-df6c-4a0b-94f6-99a56db8abb7/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/2f358c3d-df6c-4a0b-94f6-99a56db8abb7/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":[],"createdAt":"2020-01-23T